# Technical SEO — desktop

Same URL as mobile. PSI/Lighthouse **Desktop**.

| Metric | Target | Tactics |
|--------|--------|---------|
| LCP | ≤2.5s | `LcpImagePreload` + hero `srcSet`/`sizes="58vw"`; `lcpHeroImageProps()` up to 1200w; `fetchPriority="high"` |
| INP | ≤200ms | rAF scroll with deduped state; carousel sentinels; light flyout handlers |
| CLS | ≤0.1 | stable sticky header; explicit image width/height |

Nav links in HTML (`lg:flex`); keyboard dropdowns; breadcrumbs on detail pages; 1440px Urdu overflow check.

Leaf pages: `leafHeroImageUrl()` at 1200w · `SanityImage` with `fetchPriority="high"` when `priority`.

